Invocation Name: engineering facts
des:
Engineering life can make you face many things in life which you never have encountered
It is both jovial and learning phase of life where we learn new things and come across bitter truths of life.
You will get to know friends who can stay for life or teach you good lessons and go.
You can participate in many events where you can overcome your fears and invent your unknown talents.
It is such a phase where if you find a perfect partner for life then it will be the beautiful years of life
In this phase all we can learn is teamwork,helping each other in assignment,team cooperation during lab exams,combined studies and also last but not least night outs where you can gather as much memories as we can.
